  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[a, bf, bt, cf, ct]\r\n(* a = 1/(8+\\[Sigma]p^2)+1/(2*\\[Sigma]q^2)\r\nbf = -pd/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)-q/(\\[Sigma]q^2);\r\nbt = I*B/hbar;\r\ncf = -B^2/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2)-pd^2/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)-q^2/(2*\\[Sigma]q^2);\r\nct = I*A/hbar; *)\r\n\r\nresult = Sqrt[Pi/a]*(Exp[cf+ct+(bf+bt)^2/(4*a)]\r\n                    +Exp[cf-ct+(bf+bt)^2/(4*a)]\r\n                    +Exp[cf+ct+(bf-bt)^2/(4*a)]\r\n                    +Exp[cf-ct+(bf-bt)^2/(4*a)])",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wexpr\"><wgraph class=\"resizable\" style=\"width:478px;height:42px;\" aspect-ratio=\"0.0870\" tabIndex=\"-1\"><img class=\"invert-brightness\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" /></wgraph></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      }
     ],
     "id": "7b48aec7-ee8b-4921-bcc1-1e2f3bcd8432"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {},
   "executionSummary": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "res = result /. Exp[arg_] :> Exp[Expand[arg]]\r\nfac = Sqrt[Pi/a]*Exp[cf + bf^2/(4*a) + bt^2/(4*a)];\r\n\r\nres2 = fac * Expand[res/fac]\r\nInputForm[res2]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wexpr\"><wgraph class=\"resizable\" style=\"width:599px;height:41px;\" aspect-ratio=\"0.0681\" tabIndex=\"-1\"><img class=\"invert-brightness\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" /></wgraph></div>",
