  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "outer =\r\n (F2^2/(4*a) - F1^2/(4*a*hbar^2)\r\n - (F1*M2*q2)/(2*a*hbar^2)\r\n - (F2*M3*q2)/(2*a)\r\n - (M2^2*q2^2)/(4*a*hbar^2)\r\n + (M3^2*q2^2)/(4*a)\r\n - p^2/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)\r\n + (p*q2)/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)\r\n - q2^2/(8*\\[Sigma]p^2)\r\n - q^2/(2*\\[Sigma]q^2)\r\n - F1^2/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2)\r\n - (F1*M2*q2)/\\[Sigma]x^2\r\n - (M2^2*q2^2)/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2));\r\n\r\n inner1 =\r\n (((I/2)*F1*F2)/(a*hbar)\r\n - M1*q2\r\n + ((I/2)*F2*M2*q2)/(a*hbar)\r\n - ((I/2)*F1*M3*q2)/(a*hbar)\r\n - ((I/2)*M2*M3*q2^2)/(a*hbar));\r\n\r\na2 = Coefficient[outer, q2, 2]\r\nb2 = Coefficient[outer, q2, 1]\r\nc2 = Coefficient[outer, q2, 0]\r\na2t = Coefficient[inner1, q2, 2]\r\nb2tp = Coefficient[inner1, q2, 1]+M1\r\nb2tm = M1\r\nc2t = Coefficient[inner1, q2, 0]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
