   "value": "replaceF2M3 = {\r\n   F2 -> (p/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)+q/\\[Sigma]q^2),\r\n   M3 -> 1/(4*\\[Sigma]q^2),\r\n   a -> (1/(8*\\[Sigma]p^2)+1/(2*\\[Sigma]q^2))\r\n};\r\n\r\nres9 = res8 /. replaceFM2;\r\nInputForm[res9]",
